url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow","html_url":"https://github.com/web-flow","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"parents":[{"sha":"801c46ffa19d2a549adc446d1f91e7484ae61edb","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/commits/801c46ffa19d2a549adc446d1f91e7484ae61edb","html_url":"https://github.com/nestjs/nest/commit/801c46ffa19d2a549adc446d1f91e7484ae61edb"}]},{"sha":"d956db4c104c22172c3466344b50c017267aca23","node_id":"C_kwDOBNMhFNoAKGQ5NTZkYjRjMTA0YzIyMTcyYzM0NjYzNDRiNTBjMDE3MjY3YWNhMjM","commit":{"author":{"name":"hbinhng","email":"me@hbinhng.dev","date":"2026-05-21T09:46:26Z"},"committer":{"name":"hbinhng","email":"me@hbinhng.dev","date":"2026-05-21T09:46:26Z"},"message":"feat(core): warn on late websocket adapter registration\n\nCalling app.useWebSocketAdapter(adapter) after app.init() has run (e.g.\nfrom any module's OnModuleInit hook) silently no-ops: the websockets\nmodule has already captured the adapter from ApplicationConfig and\nbootstrapped the gateways. The provided adapter is stored on the config\nbut never applied — gateways remain bound to whatever adapter was active\nduring init(), which in practice is the default IoAdapter.\n\nTrack this with an isWsModuleRegistered flag flipped after\nsocketModule.register() succeeds, and emit a Logger.warn from\nuseWebSocketAdapter() when called too late. The adapter is still set on\nApplicationConfig so any code path that inspects it post-hoc keeps the\nexisting behaviour — the warning only surfaces the timing mismatch so\nconsumers can move the call to main.ts before app.init() / app.listen().\n\nCloses #16992","tree":{"sha":"c1382ab65ccb8222f8f16b17cb3917a64ee80f44","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/git/trees/c1382ab65ccb8222f8f16b17cb3917a64ee80f44"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/git/commits/d956db4c104c22172c3466344b50c017267aca23","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":true,"reason":"valid","signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\niHUEABYKAB0WIQRUJ+9DplLdOuz9D6XbDucOufL57QUCag7UcwAKCRDbDucOufL5\n7VLoAQDCUwTAku+0JjcP6bV1e8naok43Xt9FSxsDpwy9nTM0ygEA9rPg1epsChIO\nRpDT6mFCIV3FdAtZzsrSOAg0zrtSpQw=\n=3KmZ\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----","payload":"tree c1382ab65ccb8222f8f16b17cb3917a64ee80f44\nparent 801c46ffa19d2a549adc446d1f91e7484ae61edb\nauthor hbinhng <me@hbinhng.dev> 1779356786 +0700\ncommitter hbinhng <me@hbinhng.dev> 1779356786 +0700\n\nfeat(core): warn on late websocket adapter registration\n\nCalling app.useWebSocketAdapter(adapter) after app.init() has run (e.g.\nfrom any module's OnModuleInit hook) silently no-ops: the websockets\nmodule has already captured the adapter from ApplicationConfig and\nbootstrapped the gateways. The provided adapter is stored on the config\nbut never applied — gateways remain bound to whatever adapter was active\nduring init(), which in practice is the default IoAdapter.\n\nTrack this with an isWsModuleRegistered flag flipped after\nsocketModule.register() succeeds, and emit a Logger.warn from\nuseWebSocketAdapter() when called too late. The adapter is still set on\nApplicationConfig so any code path that inspects it post-hoc keeps the\nexisting behaviour — the warning only surfaces the timing mismatch so\nconsumers can move the call to main.ts before app.init() / app.listen().\n\nCloses #16992\n","verified_at":"2026-05-21T09:46:34Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/commits/d956db4c104c22172c3466344b50c017267aca23","html_url":"https://github.com/nestjs/nest/commit/d956db4c104c22172c3466344b50c017267aca23","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/commits/d956db4c104c22172c3466344b50c017267aca23/comments","author":{"login":"hbinhng","id":44113587,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ0MTEzNTg3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/44113587?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng","html_url":"https://github.com/hbinhng","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"committer":{"login":"hbinhng","id":44113587,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ0MTEzNTg3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/44113587?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng","html_url":"https://github.com/hbinhng","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hbinhng/orgs","repos_url"